Package: pqcDyber
Title: Post-Quantum Cryptography Bindings
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dyber, Inc.", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "info@dyber.com"))
Description: R bindings for the libpqc-dyber post-quantum cryptography library,
    providing access to ML-KEM, ML-DSA, and other post-quantum algorithms
    standardized by NIST.
